The commando for generating a free-sacel network is barabasi.game()

# This should approximately yield the correct exponent 3
g <- barabasi.game(1000) # increase this number to have a better estimate
plot(g,vertex.label=NA)

d <- degree(g, mode="in")
hist(d)

fit1 <- fit_power_law(d+1, 10)
fit2 <- fit_power_law(d+1, 10, implementation="R.mle")

fit1$alpha
## [1] 2.765823
stats4::coef(fit2)
##    alpha 
## 2.766205
fit1$logLik
## [1] -55.28507
stats4::logLik(fit2)
## 'log Lik.' -55.28499 (df=1)
